reviews.title: Not good.
reviews.comment: I can boot my laptop, sign in, and do everything I need before the app even finishes checking my password. For an app that\'s supposed to offer convenience, it does a horrible job. And why does it need all these permissions? Access to protected storage, access to phone and calling,  etc. Wtf? You shouldn\'t need my phone calls or my device storage to check a bank account.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Does not work
reviews.comment: I have yet to be able to do anything productive with this app. Occasionally, I\'m able to check my balance but, anything outside of that is useless. Lately, all I get from the app when I try to log in is \"your session has expired.\"
reviews.author: Kerry Sellers
